{"tid":1474822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"條片我笑到gap gap 聲","createTime":"2019-08-15T09:57:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T13:00:33.000Z","uid":205482,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a3104052b4cbdce557d883283e573fbd6f49a1","tid":1474822,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:57:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B1LDZqzFatw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1LDZqzFatw&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=6ca4ff2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB1LDZqzFatw&h=8627d727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B1LDZqzFatw</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手教育下啲5毛 挽救1%的大陸人<br />\nBtw條片我笑到gap gap 聲<br />\n化敵為友<br />\n拯救籠中鳥<br />\n<br />\n相信有部分大陸人係有理智能夠作批判性思考:<br />\n<br />\n811警暴連環<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n⒈蓄意謀殺女救護員 影片直證布袋鉛彈 爆眼球永久失明 面骨碎裂；&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n⒉插贜竹枝 造偽證 誣陷被捕者；&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n⒊地鐡站內 水平發射催淚彈CS神經毒氣；&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n⒋警喬裝示威者 帶頭發動衝擊；&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n⒌普通話軍人 多處滲透潛伏武統；&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n⒍一米內行刑 掃射胡椒彈槍、險釀電梯人踩人；&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n⒎縱容北角荃灣黑幫橫行 毆打記者路人示威者；&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n⒏濫暴痛毆 重創被捕者 打掉門牙 血肉模糊，今證實周日被捕人士被移送羅湖文錦渡拘留，後各有骨折、斷手、斷背、頸椎移位等傷勢；&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n⒐屋村老人民居範圍 發射催淚彈 CS神經毒氣；&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n１０. 殘害救護員、救護員舉旗警告 警尖沙咀阻礙救援 違反國際人道法 屬嚴重刑事罪行；&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n721元朗 警黑勾結 車廂毆打平民 不了了之&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n805過分武力 多區發放合共800催淚彈 140橡膠子彈 民區居民不滿 下區聲討&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n天水圍以男警拘捕女士 並扯走下裝 露出內褲 拖行回警察&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n數之不盡、官官相衛、指鹿為馬、漠視警例、無法制衡、無需問責、厚顏無恥。&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n若未來執法部門依然如此故我，私相授受、官官相衛，苦的 是香港未來下一代下幾代，點點被剝奪的透明法制、三權分立，向市民負責等等如同謊言。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果無腦嘅就由佢:<br />\n<br />\n818上午10時天安門廣場見！聲援香港警察！反對恐怖主義！反對迫害記者！支持言論自由！"},{"pid":"3c65ce2bb1207354eff623717e65f341c6cb8859","tid":1474822,"uid":205482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球.<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內，近距離開槍射擊<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n6. 警犬在太古站推人落電梯<br />\n7. 荃灣攻擊平民<br />\n8. 銅鑼灣警察偽裝成示威者, 拘捕時把示威者的門牙撞斷, 在示威者表示投降時還暴力地壓著他的頭部, 增加傷勢"},{"pid":"8522d36978b59fff612a9508caa9448b4c4fb8c5","tid":1474822,"uid":205482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:59:07.000Z","msg":"818"},{"pid":"8ab4178a9f0c217c07955b8118c2cfffdfdcdb87","tid":1474822,"uid":205482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"團結 不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"f5592a8968bf83db446f6143e187d13a8b9c5ca7","tid":1474822,"uid":205482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:03:51.000Z","msg":"香港人加油！"},{"pid":"883fcdfcebc4cc8c618aaa9bbdad07d7af99fa45","tid":1474822,"uid":131168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"721"}]}